Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:16.69,1:30:20.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Multi-celled organisms\nare metabolic creatures.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:20.16,1:30:24.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, life is maintained\nas a result of new cells...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:24.23,1:30:26.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...replacing dying cells.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:26.26,1:30:30.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There are also cells that never die\nand replicate indefinitely.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:30.57,1:30:31.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,These are the cancer cells.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:34.64,1:30:36.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we can satisfy two conditions...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:36.81,1:30:39.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that of maintaining indefinite\ncell replication...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:39.61,1:30:42.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and of gaining control\nover replication...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:42.71,1:30:45.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...then people will be able to\nattain immortality.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:46.02,1:30:50.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This was made possible\nthrough alchemy in medieval Europe.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:51.09,1:30:52.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Master Gen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:52.39,1:30:53.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Master Gen?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:54.19,1:30:55.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:56.16,1:30:58.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please get yourself ready.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:00.60,1:31:01.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Master Gen...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:04.87,1:31:07.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:10.21,1:31:11.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The cherry blossoms.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:13.28,1:31:15.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But haven't they already...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:19.12,1:31:21.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!\NWhat a fright, Master Gen!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:22.09,1:31:24.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You surprised me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:24.25,1:31:27.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought\nmy heart was going to stop.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:27.72,1:31:30.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, will you please\nget yourself ready?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:34.33,1:31:35.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Master Gen!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:35.97,1:31:37.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't do that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:38.33,1:31:39.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to go...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:39.74,1:31:40.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:41.40,1:31:42.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Master Gen!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:46.94,1:31:48.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Master Gen!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:50.18,1:31:52.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't, Master Gen!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:52.35,1:31:54.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't do this!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:01.26,1:32:02.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't, Master Gen!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:02.89,1:32:04.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:06.76,1:32:09.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be late for college!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:22.48,1:32:25.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When Gen's eyes turn golden...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:25.15,1:32:27.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...he's like a runaway train.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:28.42,1:32:30.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His metabolic rate runs amuck...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:30.35,1:32:31.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and just before he expires...??
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:32.19,1:32:36.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is why his semen turns gold and\nhe cannot control his libido.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:37.29,1:32:39.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's his fate.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:39.16,1:32:42.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The fate of the Hiraga bloodline.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:42.63,1:32:44.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because he will not live long...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:44.87,1:32:47.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...his blood urges him on...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:48.00,1:32:51.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...to produce a progeny.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:51.44,1:32:57.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All for the sake of the eternally\nblossoming cherry trees.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:05.26,1:33:07.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't\nfor the immortality gene...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:07.56,1:33:10.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Gen's overheated metabolic rate\ncould be stemmed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:10.53,1:33:11.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:11.63,1:33:13.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right with you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:13.60,1:33:16.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of asking me now?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:16.53,1:33:21.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want Gen to be able to live\nthe life of a normal person...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:22.04,1:33:25.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and break free from the cursed\nfate of the Hiraga family.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:26.84,1:33:31.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't ever want to feel\nthat sorrow and despair again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:32.55,1:33:34.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If he could live out his life...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:34.95,1:33:36.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I would be happy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:44.29,1:33:46.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you, Beth?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:47.90,1:33:50.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing! It's really nothing!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:50.83,1:33:51.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't have!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:51.90,1:33:52.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:06.22,1:34:07.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hiraga?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:11.39,1:34:13.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could you excuse me for a minute?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:14.59,1:34:17.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hiraga,\nwhat time do you think it is?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:17.66,1:34:19.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so late for college?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:21.26,1:34:22.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:25.67,1:34:29.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?\NYour eye color's different.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:29.41,1:34:30.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, prez...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:30.54,1:34:31.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:31.61,1:34:32.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:37.61,1:34:40.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:55.57,1:34:57.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop that!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:57.67,1:34:58.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hiraga!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:59.20,1:35:00.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Check that out!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:00.67,1:35:02.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty bold!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:02.14,1:35:02.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:04.54,1:35:06.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No! Please stop!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:06.98,1:35:08.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:11.25,1:35:12.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hiraga!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:14.02,1:35:15.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:27.13,1:35:28.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hiraga!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:31.00,1:35:32.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:34.84,1:35:36.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:48.95,1:35:51.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Ms. Rokuhira.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:51.59,1:35:52.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:54.32,1:35:55.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:55.46,1:35:56.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:57.16,1:35:59.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could you leave the two of us alone?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:59.23,1:36:00.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This man's in danger.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:05.50,1:36:06.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:52.01,1:36:58.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd be the one\nlooking in from the outside.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:58.45,1:36:59.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Ito?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:00.29,1:37:05.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh...\NI have a stomachache again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:05.60,1:37:08.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it later. I'm busy now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:08.70,1:37:09.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:10.27,1:37:11.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:11.43,1:37:15.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me?\NNow, go back to your class.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:16.91,1:37:18.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:23.31,1:37:24.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:24.51,1:37:28.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...there's no room for me\nin there right now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:29.32,1:37:30.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:30.65,1:37:32.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:32.89,1:37:34.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All of your fears...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:34.69,1:37:36.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and sorrows...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:36.39,1:37:39.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I will receive them all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:39.83,1:37:42.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forget all of those,\njust for now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:43.37,1:37:46.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've done nothing wrong.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:50.63,1:38:52.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is this feeling?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:53.34,1:38:57.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I remember\nbeing held like this before.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:57.77,1:38:58.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:59.18,1:39:00.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:00.31,1:39:01.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that was...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:01.61,1:39:02.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the one in my dreams...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:04.08,1:39:07.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the woman I saw\nunder the cherry tree.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:07.38,1:39:08.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:09.25,1:39:10.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Sakurako!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:25.50,1:39:26.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Sakurako...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:41.32,1:39:44.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, Ms. Sakurako?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:14.58,1:40:17.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have you woken up?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:20.69,1:40:21.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:22.73,1:40:25.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:26.46,1:40:28.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Am I sick?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:29.70,1:40:31.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this for?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:32.20,1:40:35.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I was at college...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:35.87,1:40:37.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...with Ms. Sakurako...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:38.81,1:40:40.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...with Ms. Sakurako...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:41.61,1:40:45.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! I did it with...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:45.92,1:40:48.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to\nfeel bad about it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:49.49,1:40:53.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all the fault of\nthe Hiraga bloodline.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:55.02,1:41:00.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sakurako knows about that\nmore than anyone else.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:01.56,1:41:02.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sakurako?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:03.73,1:41:06.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally about to end.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:07.00,1:41:10.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The ominous curse\nof the Hiraga bloodline...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:10.81,1:41:12.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and your suffering.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:13.28,1:41:14.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:15.11,1:41:16.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...suffering?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:17.25,1:41:19.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's an ancient, ancient story.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:20.72,1:41:24.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One of the early ancestors of the Hiraga...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:24.35,1:41:27.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...obtained immortality using...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:27.12,1:41:30.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the methods of alchemy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:33.23,1:41:34.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:34.83,1:41:39.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...perhaps as retribution\nfor violating the laws of nature...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:39.60,1:41:45.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that ancestor was the only one\nwho became immortal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:45.54,1:41:47.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All of the children and\ngrandchildren...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:48.11,1:41:50.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...died of unknown causes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:50.88,1:41:55.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There was a serious defect\nin the genes of the descendants.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:56.55,1:42:00.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. As with your mother...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:00.49,1:42:02.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and with you right now...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:02.86,1:42:07.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...it had wrecked\nthe wheels of nature.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:07.40,1:42:10.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about, Grandma?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:10.77,1:42:14.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Realizing the gravity\nof the sin committed...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:14.57,1:42:16.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that ancestor began\nlooking into ways...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:16.84,1:42:21.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...of returning those children's\nphysical conditions...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:21.28,1:42:25.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...to their normal states.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:25.92,1:42:28.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That ancestor had met a woman...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:28.55,1:42:32.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...who came from a legendary European\nfamily known for its immortality.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:33.09,1:42:36.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And after meeting with scholars\nwho studied...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:36.86,1:42:41.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the nature of immortality\nfrom a scientific perspective...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:41.43,1:42:45.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...a treatment was finally uncovered.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:47.70,1:42:48.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:51.87,1:42:55.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To live forever...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:55.88,1:42:58.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...means that all of\nthe sufferings of life...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:58.78,1:43:02.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...also continue forever.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:02.35,1:43:05.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is the fate that I have had to...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:05.82,1:43:07.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...bear.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:07.56,1:43:08.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:09.83,1:43:11.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My selfish...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:11.83,1:43:13.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...disgraceful desire...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:13.86,1:43:18.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...had resulted in the suffering\nof all of the Hiraga.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:18.60,1:43:20.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:20.60,1:43:21.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:22.34,1:43:24.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:46.43,1:43:48.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:50.33,1:43:52.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Sakurako.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:54.44,1:43:55.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:55.97,1:43:57.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...woman of my...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:58.01,1:43:59.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...dreams.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:05.48,1:44:08.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I intended to keep up the charade...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:09.02,1:44:12.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...of the masked grandmother\nuntil the end.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:12.69,1:44:13.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:13.96,1:44:16.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...out of some capricious need...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:16.23,1:44:20.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I revealed myself to you\nas Sakurako.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:21.33,1:44:25.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you would remember.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:25.97,1:44:28.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just once, 1 2 years ago.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:28.94,1:44:33.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The night when your mother\NSakurako brought you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:51.56,1:44:52.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Sakura?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:00.94,1:45:05.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You promised not to show yourself\nin front of Gen!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:26.96,1:45:31.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is all the result of my errors.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:32.27,1:45:36.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did I play with\nthe lives of people...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:37.01,1:45:42.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but I had also\ncommitted a grave sin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:42.88,1:45:44.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am the capricious ancestor...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:44.95,1:45:48.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...who caused such damage\nto the family.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:50.22,1:45:51.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:52.49,1:45:54.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After this...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:54.49,1:45:57.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...you will go toJennifer's university.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:57.26,1:46:00.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And you will receive treatment.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:00.63,1:46:04.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They will keep your symptoms\nin check with medications.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:04.53,1:46:06.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And over time...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:06.37,1:46:09.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...they will gradually\nbring your body back to normal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:10.24,1:46:11.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You will live a life...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:12.01,1:46:15.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...separate from Beth and myself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:15.94,1:46:20.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You will not hold on to\nthe vestiges of our past.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:21.35,1:46:27.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've revealed myself\nfrom behind this unsightly visage.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:32.96,1:46:35.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:37.93,1:46:39.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:03.19,1:47:04.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:04.73,1:47:08.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...she hides behind her mask\N'til the end anyway.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:11.13,1:47:12.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:20.51,1:47:21.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:22.64,1:47:24.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met before?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:25.95,1:47:28.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is your relationship with him?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:28.55,1:47:29.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Him?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:30.25,1:47:31.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen Hiraga.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:31.99,1:47:34.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My relationship with Gen...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:34.62,1:47:36.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:36.43,1:47:40.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You did have sex\nbehind the campus 2 months ago.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:40.40,1:47:42.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You saw that?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:42.33,1:47:45.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is your relationship with him?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:45.37,1:47:47.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you to Gen, anyway?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:47.94,1:47:49.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:49.64,1:47:50.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the class president.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:53.04,1:47:55.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is Mr. Hiraga all right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:56.15,1:47:58.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't normal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:58.15,1:48:00.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even today, his eyes were all golden...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:00.95,1:48:02.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How much do you know?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:02.75,1:48:04.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:04.29,1:48:07.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you know something,\nplease tell me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:07.16,1:48:08.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:08.32,1:48:11.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...happened to Gen Hiraga?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:15.00,1:48:17.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure this is all right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:18.90,1:48:22.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that you did not order me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:22.47,1:48:26.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to use the cursed\npower of my family...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:26.41,1:48:28.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Master Gen would be all right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:28.88,1:48:33.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Jennifer Collins' help\nwould not be necessary.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:34.02,1:48:35.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You would've been...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:35.55,1:48:39.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...able to continue living\nwith Master Gen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:39.92,1:48:40.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:41.96,1:48:45.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen and I were\nnever supposed to meet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:45.96,1:48:48.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Living together...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:49.06,1:48:51.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...was always forbidden.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:52.37,1:48:56.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you\ntake Master Gen in?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:56.81,1:48:58.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Taking the name of Sakurako...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:58.54,1:49:02.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and revealing yourself\nto Master Gen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:03.51,1:49:05.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You must have\nhad feelings for him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:07.98,1:49:11.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the reason\nwhy people live...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:11.55,1:49:15.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...they certainly are creatures\nthat bear heavy burdens.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:15.22,1:49:16.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:16.56,1:49:20.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I cannot force this man to suffer...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:20.23,1:49:23.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the same lives we have.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:23.37,1:49:27.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen must have the same purpose\nas an ordinary human.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:27.57,1:49:31.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is, the happiness\nthat comes from being normal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:31.97,1:49:33.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is something...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:33.84,1:49:36.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that you and I lost long ago.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:56.10,1:49:57.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:57.73,1:49:58.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:59.77,1:50:01.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Grandma.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:02.17,1:50:05.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be separated.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:05.64,1:50:08.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want us to stay together forever.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:08.91,1:50:09.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:10.65,1:50:12.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to separate?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:13.25,1:50:15.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever you may be, Grandma...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:15.28,1:50:16.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I am...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:17.99,1:50:20.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, Gen...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:21.49,1:50:22.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:23.43,1:50:25.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We only just met.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:25.56,1:50:29.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was a mistake in the first place.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:29.50,1:50:31.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:31.57,1:50:33.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:33.40,1:50:35.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...it was strange.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:35.24,1:50:39.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it,\nthe same dream over and over.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:39.47,1:50:44.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I realize that was\nsomething that actually happened.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:44.58,1:50:46.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:47.72,1:50:49.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:49.32,1:50:51.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...when you held me in your arms.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:52.82,1:50:54.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I remember.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:54.89,1:50:58.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You smelled the same as my mother.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:59.33,1:51:00.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:02.60,1:51:04.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:04.60,1:51:06.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that we've met again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:10.57,1:51:12.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:13.14,1:51:16.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From that time on...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:16.45,1:51:19.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't, Gen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:19.35,1:51:22.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we first met\nunder that cherry tree...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:22.52,1:51:23.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...on that night...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:26.09,1:51:28.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I have always loved you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:35.93,1:51:36.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:46.21,1:51:47.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:48.88,1:51:49.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:13.34,1:52:14.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're beautiful...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:15.30,1:52:16.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Grandma.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:21.84,1:52:24.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The same scent as my mother's.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:25.41,1:52:27.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I sensed it even in my dreams.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:27.78,1:52:30.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The same face as my mother's.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:31.05,1:52:32.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The same warmth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:33.36,1:52:34.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When she...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:35.19,1:52:37.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...when Sakurako gave birth to you...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:37.86,1:52:41.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...she was a daughter\nwho resembled me very much.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:41.96,1:52:44.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Gen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:45.07,1:52:49.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even you show a resemblance\nto another ancestor...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:49.47,1:52:51.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...who lived long ago...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:51.81,1:52:54.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and remains\ndeep within my memory.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:03.89,1:53:05.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You must have been lonely...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:05.82,1:53:06.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...until now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:07.52,1:53:10.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You are a kind man.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:11.16,1:53:14.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We will remain together forever.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:14.43,1:53:16.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like a dream.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:16.83,1:53:17.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a dream!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:19.10,1:53:20.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:21.07,1:53:22.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...dream.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:28.28,1:53:31.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really my grandma?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:31.71,1:53:35.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am your grandmother's...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:35.25,1:53:36.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...grandmother's...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:36.92,1:53:39.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...grandmother.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:42.92,1:53:45.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid of me, Gen?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:54.30,1:53:56.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am the cherry tree.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:57.54,1:54:01.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The tree rooted in the garden\nwhere our family sleeps.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:01.14,1:54:03.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A cherry tree that never wilts...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:03.98,1:54:05.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...blossoming forever.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:17.35,1:55:18.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hiraga!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:40.84,1:55:45.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you could at least stay\nuntil graduation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:47.15,1:55:51.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You will come back\nwhen you're better, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:53.99,1:55:56.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like we'll never meet again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:59.33,1:56:01.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll phone you when I get there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:01.63,1:56:03.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write you too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:10.87,1:56:12.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take care.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:20.82,1:56:23.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,- I guess this is it, Hiraga--\N- Ooops!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:25.32,1:56:26.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:26.82,1:56:28.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You too,Jennifer?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:28.89,1:56:31.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandmother did\nask me to watch over you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:31.79,1:56:34.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'm going back to\ngraduate college.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:34.80,1:56:37.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say\NI'm like your guardian.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:38.53,1:56:40.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With physical relationships.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:40.50,1:56:42.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop that...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:42.27,1:56:43.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:43.71,1:56:46.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do lots of research\nwhen we get there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:46.64,1:56:47.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:47.54,1:56:49.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it like that!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:54.58,1:56:55.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:55.55,1:56:58.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,- You're crazy! Do you have a ticket?\N- What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:58.25,1:56:59.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from Hiraga!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:00.06,1:57:02.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was just kidding.\NThat's the trouble with virgins.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:03.09,1:57:04.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a virgin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:22.24,1:57:24.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Still in bloom...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:25.15,1:57:27.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the cherry blossoms.
